{"tid":330978,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【警疑濫權溝女】女友疑被男警滋擾 大學男連串投訴","createTime":"2017-07-21T17:08:57.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-22T04:44:02.000Z","uid":23479,"like":33,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b6059f84a21db26b477687b74b86478d1d93cc5b","tid":330978,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"0:00<br />\n<br />\n「那天晚上我回家後，就上網查閱，看看怎樣投訴。」正就讀大學的Alan表示，由於懷疑該名警員假公濟私「溝女」，事後即展開連串投訴行動。&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAlan說：「那天晚上，我上申訴專員公署的網頁投訴，匯報了這事件。翌日，我帶女友到警察投訴課及個人私隱專員公署辦理投訴事情，都是針對這件事作出投訴。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n事件對女友造成什麼困擾？「她本來覺得協助警方是很普通事情，但之後竟然被問到這樣奇怪問題，就覺得有點尷尬，覺得警察不應這樣做。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\nAlan怎樣看這事呢？「我覺得本是小事，但他可以取我女友電話號碼，即是有機會打其他女孩子主意，這亦是我覺得要投訴的最大原因。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n會否覺得那名警員濫用職權？「我覺得是，因為給了警員個人資料，是基於警民信任，但他竟然以私人理由聯絡我女友，我覺得是某程度上破壞了這信任。」&nbsp;<br />\n<br />\n警方回覆稱，投訴警察課已接獲相關投訴，會按既定程序公平公正處理，現階段不作評論。<br />\n<br />\n大律師陸偉雄建議，女事主可向涉事警員的部門主管查詢，他們現在的調查內容是否有需要問到這些私人問題，如部門主管答不需要，該名警員就屬於假公濟私和濫用職權。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_532214_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_532214_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&d=CKgDxfPOCJFUynQvfp2Tj4sQCuff2cTRbXvS6e969MQ%3D&h=928e697b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhkm.appledaily.com%2Fdetail.php%3Fguid%3D2_532214_0%26category_guid%3Dnextplus%26category%3Dmagazine&h=566140fe\" target=\"_blank\">http://hkm.appledaily.com/detail.php?guid=2_532214_0&amp;category_guid=nextplus&amp;category=magazine</a>"},{"pid":"929e660c7dfd9d7164164f3b5c051d6377a3631e","tid":330978,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T17:13:41.000Z","msg":"仙人狙擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ea21d9afe5b18ac5defcd3f4998237ef56f34d1d","tid":330978,"uid":73202,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:36:33.000Z","msg":"狗公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79783458a80d65f27e8beab06d84b44078b68097","tid":330978,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:39:11.000Z","msg":"警厹<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8801099c1eb7ba58b3089081b7af3c2cfc5c4731","tid":330978,"uid":7790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T18:51:02.000Z","msg":"推到條廢柴守水塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac17c7ac68a55763e6a70c7e06457562280da6f3","tid":330978,"uid":55913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T19:48:50.000Z","msg":"乜野警隊非常重視⋯⋯段野呢？"},{"pid":"97a2a2a5445712a45ff5961d723c29c20865bbf6","tid":330978,"uid":35831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T19:50:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>推到條廢柴守水塘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有冇得守水塘呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec7ac69e8404ed51eb6fc69f6288593e3b7f6748","tid":330978,"uid":25148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T20:20:00.000Z","msg":"仙人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"861997d0ab6fe781ce6e89bd3b354c9ef585be9b","tid":330978,"uid":1790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-21T20:28:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>乜野警隊非常重視⋯⋯段野呢？</blockquote><br />\n開file先用咋<br />\n今次直頭close file<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b29533039cff5bde09a9f8a19839cc0ff784466","tid":330978,"uid":23479,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-22T04:44:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}